{"tid":967010,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥倫比亞業餘聯賽都有VAR了！英超到現在還不用...","createTime":"2019-01-03T08:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T08:36:20.000Z","uid":53121,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32218af972fa4d18a3255cc4e6c2cbe8f6b70823","tid":967010,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:07:57.000Z","msg":"VAR在足壇的應用越來越普及，五大聯賽中除了英超之外，都已經啟用了這項視頻回放技術。甚至在業餘聯賽中，也有球迷自製了VAR。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/2019/01/03/bac4ace4ec8142b0a88ca4eaffd8711f.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2F2019%2F01%2F03%2Fbac4ace4ec8142b0a88ca4eaffd8711f.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=a0fa1d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在哥倫比亞的一個小鎮裡的一場業餘比賽中，球迷用廢棄的電腦屏幕製作了一個簡陋的VAR，還在外面包裹了一個紙箱，上面寫著&ldquo;VAR&rdquo;三個字母。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/2019/01/03/03e5e1540dfc445fa4db81dba2d1e9c2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2F2019%2F01%2F03%2F03e5e1540dfc445fa4db81dba2d1e9c2.gif&h=6980d36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裁判在觀看了這個自製VAR後，吹罰進球有效。"},{"pid":"29cbe073f3ab59c8deea4599c58cc100e0ea6034","tid":967010,"uid":55421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvPRqvF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvPRqvF.png&h=29bb5722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a6686dadcab1f154c5eea04fe51376e7e7d3ae","tid":967010,"uid":215270,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"29cbe073f3ab59c8deea4599c58cc100e0ea6034","tid":967010,"uid":55421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvPRqvF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvPRqvF.png&h=29bb5722&s={SIZE}\" />